OL,3,CMore than 85,000 motorists exceed
OL,4,C20mph speed limit
OL,6,FMore than 85,000 motorists were last
OL,7,Fyear caught exceeding the 20mph speed
OL,8,Flimit.
OL,10,FFigures from GoSafe show the majority
OL,11,Fwere in Mid and South Wales. August
OL,12,Fsaw the most offences. The average
OL,13,Fspeed was 28mph.
OL,15,FGoSafe says enforcement in 20mph areas
OL,16,Fstarted to be reintroduced at the
OL,17,Fbeginning of November 2023. This was
OL,18,Fin existing 20mph enforcement
OL,19,Flocations that weren't affected by a
OL,20,Flegislation change and had the correct
OL,21,Fsignage in place.
