OL,3,CMore than 85,000 motorists exceed
OL,4,C20mph speed limit
OL,6,FGoSafe temporarily suspended 20mph
OL,7,Fenforcement in September 2023 after
OL,8,Fthe law change. It says the decision
OL,9,Fwas made for several reasons. This
OL,10,Fincluded allowing people time to
OL,11,Fadjust to the change, to allow
OL,12,FHighways authorities to adjust road
OL,13,Fsignage and Traffic Regulation Orders
OL,14,F(TRO), and due to roadside engagement
OL,15,Fsessions being prioritised.
